data.description: Situated on .24 acres, this 3 bed, 1 bath home provides the potential for investment income with the attached 2 bed, 1 bath attached ADU. The main home boasts an updated kitchen, and newer exterior paint, skylights, and roof (July 2022). The attached ADU has a private entrance, and its own yard space, while boasting 2 bedrooms, 1 bath and a kitchenette. Providing space and privacy for an in-law suite, rental income or extended family. Located within a short distance of the American River, Ancil Hoffman park, restaurants, and award-winning schools this home awaits its next owner.
